WINDOWS:
You can use coin controls to combine your amounts, this will require re-maturing your coins for 510 blocks though (about 8 hours) before staking starts again
settings  - display - "display coin control features (experts only!)"
then go to your Send Coins section, click "inputs" button
list mode - tick all coin amounts, click okay
send to yourself (any of your receiving addresses), copy the "after fee" amount and send that to your address

MAC:
Click on peepcoin-qt > preferences > display > coin control
then go to your Send Coins section, click "inputs" button
list mode - tick all coin amounts, click okay
send to yourself (any of your receiving addresses), copy the "after fee" amount and send that to your address
